quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  28,51,"Goo…óii Min hewtinii …ďe Konngol ngol, mbelejo'o, …ďe mbaajitora."
  28,52,"∆Āen …ďe Min ndokki Deftere [Tawreeta] nden, ko adii [Alqur'aana] ndee, ko …ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe nde."
  28,53,"Si nde janngaama e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'a: "Min ngooŇč…óinii nde. Ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi amen. Pellet min woniino jebbilii…ďe, ado mayre"."
  28,54,"∆Āeen …óon, …ďe jonniroyte njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin, laabi …ói…ói, sabu ko …ďe mu√Īinoo kon, he…ďe ndu√Īiraynoo mo∆ī∆īere nden, bone on, e hu'unde nde Min ngarsiki …ďe nden, he…ďe nafqa."
  28,55,"Si …ďe nanii meerente, …ďe …óuurnoo e …óum, …ďe mbi'a: "Ko minen golle amen ngoodani, ko onon kadi golle mon nhoodani. Kisal wonii e mo'on. Min …óa…ď…ďataa wonndugol e majju…ďe …ďen"."
  28,56,"Pellet, an (Nulaa…óo), a feewnata mo nji…ó…óaa; kono Alla no feewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko KaŇčko …ďuri anndude feew…ďe …ďen."
  28,57,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Si min njokkidii peewal ngal e maa, men biftete ka leydi amen". E Min ho…óiniraali …ďe e nokku horminaa…óo, koolnii…óo, mo dim…óe noone kaka addetee e mun, arsike immorde ka Amen? Si ko woni, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe nganndaa."
  28,58,"∆äuu…óii ko Min kakli, e yim…ďe ca'e, bewrunoo…ďe nguuree mum, e homo non galleeji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ko…óiraaka …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, si wonaa see…óa. Min laatii wonn'de ronoo…ďe …ďeen."
  28,59,"Joomi maa siforaali won'de kalkoowo yim…ďe ca'e, haa O immina e le√Īol ma…ď…ďe…óen, Nulaa…óo, ko janngana …ďe aayeeje Amen …óen. Min siforaali kadi kalkugol yim…ďe ca'e, si wonaa hara yim…ďe majje ko too√Īu…ďe."